Why we use decortor pattern ?
we use it to avoid class explosion


BasePizza
FarmHouse        ->  is  - a  -> BasePizza
VefDelight       ->  is  - a  -> BasePizza
ToppingDecorator ->  is  - a  -> BasePizza
ExtraCheese      ->  is  - a  -> ToppingDecorator
Mushroom         ->  is  - a  -> ToppingDecorator
ExtraCheese      ->  has - a  -> BasePizza
Mushroom         ->  has - a  -> BasePizza